# Style of comment
+----------------------------------
 Bee has support for:
   ** Single line comments
   -- End of line comments
   |: Nested comments     :|
   |: Expression comments :|
   |: Debug-code comments :|
----------------------------------+

## rule
rule main:
  ** Single line comment
  pass; -- end of line comment
  ...

  ** Expression comments
print ("comments     |: expression:|
        are working  |: comments  :|
        in strings"  |: are useful:|
        ); 
return;
